title: Large, classic 1 bedroom at Windsor Arms (202)!
map_address: 532 Belmont Ave E near Belmont and Mercer
posting_body: ['Spacious 1 bedroom apartment at The Windsor Arms.', 'This classic and charming brick building is perfectly situated in Capitol Hill – tucked away on a quiet, residential quarter of this urban neighborhood, but within an easy stroll to all the offerings on Broadway and beyond, including grocery stores, gyms, library, parks, and an array of restaurants, bars, cafes, and boutiques.', 'This 2nd floor 1 bed / 1 bath features:', 'Hardwood floors', 'Spacious kitchen with ample cabinet space', 'Full-sized bathtub and shower', 'Thermostat-controlled baseboard heat', 'Four large closets!', 'Windows are north and west facing', 'Reasonable flat fee for utilities: $75 (second occupant fee of $35) (Water, sewer, garbage, and hot water)', 'The building offers on-site laundry (with convenient pay-by-phone feature), parking (based on availability), bike storage, and remote intercom entry.', 'Cats are welcome.', 'Sorry, no dogs.', 'Minimum credit score: 700', 'Text or email to schedule a tour.']
